body:
I am very annoyed by the announcement the new Urgot rework will be effectively removing two of the existing skins, Butcher Urgot is losing the defining feature of the skin, the stitched together human skin mask which i purchased the skin for, whilst giant enemy crabgot is shifting in tone from a humorous costume to an actual crustacean of some description. Riot has justified many of their recent visual reworks not featuring a &quot;classic&quot; skin because the recent reworks have stayed closer to the original champion&#039;s visual theme, but in this case they have failed to deliver that for two of urgot&#039;s skins!
Please riot, give Butcher back his proper mask and consider using that weird sea monster thing as a separate skin to the beloved crabgot!
{{champion:6}}
